                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-04-06</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>If you indeed want to take this journey, a good starting point is "Autobiography of a Yogi" by Swami Paramahamsa Yogananda.<P>I don't need to say anymore, you will figure it out for yourself.</span>
                  
              
